snippet.title: Amico™ Deep Dive - Intellivision® Shark! Shark!
snippet.description:
Join hosts Tommy Tallarico and John Alvarado as they walk you through an in-depth review of Intellivision® Shark! Shark! as part of Intellivision’s new Deep Dive video series. Each video will take a comprehensive look at individual Amico titles, providing viewers with history, insight and tips and tricks about gameplay. 

Thank you for watching and don't forget to LIKE and SUBSCRIBE!

Make sure to visit our website:  https://www.intellivision.com
And don't forget to sign up to our Mailing List:  https://intellivision.com/subscribe
Facebook:  https://www.facebook.com/Intellivision
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/Intellivision
Subscribe to our YouTube channel:  https://www.youtube.com/Intellivision


Footage shown may not represent final materials. Graphics and features subject to change.
